snippet.title: Gta 5 All Weapons Locations | Story Mode | Unlimited Ammo Glitch 2022 (PS5/4/3, XBox One/X/S, PC)
snippet.description:
Hey what's up you guys, im back with another tutorial on Gta V! So today I'm gonna show you how to find Weapons for free in Gta 5 Story Mode(offline) with the exact spawn locations that you can find around Los Santos. Also the glitch shown in the video can be used to collect unlimited ammo for the found Weapons.

You'll find almost everything you need to know upto date because im playing on one of the latest version which is 1.57(1.58 is the most recent one) and i can ensure that these locations and methods are working across most of the platforms including ps5, ps4, ps3 xbox one, xbox series x, xbox 360 and pc(which im demonstrating).

This is what i found so far

Weapons:
▫️Carbine Riffle
▫️Assault Riffle
▫️Sniper Riffle
▫️SMG
▫️MG
▫️Minigun
▫️Pump Shotgun
▫️Sawed off Shotgun
▫️Assault Shotgun
▫️Heavy Grenade Launcher

Other:
▫️Grenade 
▫️Sticky Bomb
▫️Molotov
▫️Baseball Bat
▫️Crowbar

►Leaving a LIKE would always appreciate! 
►Subscribe for latest video uploads! http://bit.ly/29ZRld9

Thanks for watching and see you back!
